::Zardus::

Zardus lands near the predacon base, gun ready. He puts away his gun as he 
fails to see any attackers other than Suukie, who seemed to be being beat up 
by several preds.

He turns to look the predacon base, raising his comm-link to his mouth.

"I don't think the treaty with the maximals is going to work out, Hell 
Beast," he says into it, "Are we going to attack the newcomers with just our 
two faction?"
